 a redirect method. The context will fire the completion handler"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the redirect completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Due to the nature of iOS, very little concrete information can be gained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"during this process, as all actions take place in either the Safari app"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or the sandboxed SFSafariViewController class. The context attempts to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detect when the user has completed the necessary redirect action by listening"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for both app foregrounds and url callbacks received in the app delegate."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, it is possible the when the redirect is “completed”, the user may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have not actually completed the necessary actions to authorize the charge.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"You should not use either this class, nor "},{"code":"STPAPIClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", as a way"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to determine when you should charge the Source or to determine if the redirect"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was successful. Use Stripe webhooks on your backend server to listen for Source"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"state changes and to make the charge."}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"STPRedirectContext"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"STPRedirectContext"}],"title":"STPRedirectContext"},"doc://com.stripe.stripe-payments-ui/documentation/StripePaymentsUI":{"title":"StripePaymentsUI","url":"\/documentation\/stripepaymentsui","type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.str